title: VeganBurg - Jalan Eunos
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out
description: VeganBurg's flagship location. Features a menu of all-vegan burgers along with fries, sides, soup and beverages. Burger patties are made from non-gmo soy bean and/or mushroom and buns are fiber-fuelled with seeds and walnuts. Free Wi-Fi.
